title: AHS: Apocalypse Episode 10 Promo Breakdown!
author: Think Story
comment: Don't forget that Marie Laveau is the one standing next to Coredlia at 1:14, which could be why Dinah looks so shocked!
I’m just hoping this episode is over 38mins long, we ( AHS fans ) deserve an episode that’s at least over a hour
Cordelia didn’t put Dinah under the spell because when Michael interviewed her she said she wasn’t powerful enough to stop anything he had planned, indicating that she knew who she was

Dinah already knew who she really was in the outpost, as you've mentioned that Cordelia returns her memories. When Dinah has her interview with Michael they acknowledge one another from their past which we've seen over the series with the latest episode revealing the deal she made. I hope Marie Laveau gives her a dressing down!
